’Щ@223954f890eee435bcd13bb3b43aaef7e89f383a2ec8a00d90373de1b65639a6Ъ"Title: title: str kebab-case
Path: Examples
Content:
convert a string to kebab-case
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> 'NuShell' | str kebab-case
nu-shell

```
convert a string to kebab-case
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> 'thisIsTheFirstCase' | str kebab-case
this-is-the-first-case

```
convert a string to kebab-case
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> 'THIS_IS_THE_SECOND_CASE' | str kebab-case
this-is-the-second-case

```
convert a column from a table to kebab-case
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
